title: Andrews government must ensure land is available to meet demand for housing
text:
Andrews government must ensure land i... Andrews government must ensure land is available to meet demand for housing 2 hrs ago Read more: Sydney Morning Herald 
About 110,000 lots, equivalent to just over seven years of land supply, are locked up in Melbourne's planning system. Is Melbourne's housing market approaching a bubble? With so much public commentary supporting and disputing the concept of a housing "bubble" you could be forgiven for swinging regularly between hysteria and hope as this debate rages.   Sydney Morning Herald.
